The Blacklight virus, created by Emperor Alexander Mercer, is a virus that turns its host's body into an extremely durable and malleable blob of biomatter. While the host typically takes on the outward appearance of a tall, muscular, and attractive human, they can shapeshift at will and their internal organs are mostly just soup. Blacklight hosts are known as Evolved, and it was their creation that led to the existence of the Cybusian Empire. They replenish themselves either by eating normal food, or by liquefying and digesting a live target using piercing tendrils and acid in a process known as Consumption.

  • Their colonial ventures in geographic area have brought in new trades such as lumber and fishing.
